            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "to generate the schema from the Swift Bundler source code as a quick fix, but",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "make sure to let me know anyway so that I can update it for everyone!",
              "type" : "text"
